  "title": "Human Resource (HR) & Admin Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Human Resource (HR) & Admin Officer</strong></p><p><strong>Company:</strong> De Beaute Beauty & Slimming<br /><br />We are a dynamic and growing organization in the Beauty, Slimming, and Spa Wellness industry, committed to fostering a positive work environment and supporting our  company's team's professional growth.</p><p><strong>Work Type: </strong>Flexible hours – Part-time or Full-time available </p><p><strong>Salary: </strong>SGD 2,500 – SGD 3,500 per month (depending on experience and qualifications)</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong><br />- Manage end-to-end recruitment and onboarding processes<br />- Maintain employee records and HR databases<br />- Handle payroll, attendance, and leave management<br />- Support the implementation of HR policies and procedures, including compliance with Singapore government laws.<br />- Organize and coordinate administrative activities<br />- Assist in employee engagement and welfare activities<br />- Able to relate and communicate with employees on company rules and  regulations<br />- Ensure compliance with labor laws and company policies<br />- Provide general administrative support to management</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />- Must have experience in Human Resources, Business Administration, or a related field<br />- Previous experience in HR and/or Admin roles preferred<br />- Strong organizational and multitasking skills<br />- Excellent communication and interpersonal abilities<br />- Proficient in MS Office and HR management systems<br />- Ability to work independently and as part of a team</p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong><br />- Flexible working hours<br />- Option to work part-time or full-time<br />- Supportive and inclusive work culture<br />- Opportunities for career growth<br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please contact us via WhatsApp at <strong>8133 3030</strong>. Initial interviews will be conducted via video call, followed by an in-person office interview.</p><p><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/new#job-description\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
